name: Funkadelic
profile:
Funkadelic is an American band most prominent during the 1970s. The band and its sister act [a8887], both led by [a=George Clinton], began the funk music culture of that decade.
Inducted into Rock And Roll Hall of Fame in 1997 (Performer).
